sequenceDiagram
    actor C as Client
    participant G as kgateway (Envoy)
    participant O as OpenPolicyAgent<br/>(ext_authz gRPC :9191)
    participant B as sample-api (Backend)

    C->>G: HTTP request<br/>(Authorization: Bearer JWT)
    Note over G: TrafficPolicy api-extauth<br/>-> GatewayExtension opa-envoy
    G->>O: CheckRequest (gRPC ext_authz)<br/>method, path, headers, body
    Note over O: policy envoy/authz/allow<br/>verify RS256 sig, exp, issuer,<br/>match scopes vs endpoint

    alt authorized (allow = true)
        O-->>G: CheckResponse OK (200)
        G->>B: forward request
        B-->>G: 200 response
        G-->>C: 200 response
    else not authorized (allow = false)
        O-->>G: CheckResponse Denied (403)
        Note over G: backend never reached
        G-->>C: 403 Forbidden
    end
